	<h2 id="removed-plugins">Removed Plugins</h2>

	<p>This shows how many plugins have been removed from the community plugin list each month. The dashed gray line is the raw data and the blue line has been smoothed.</p>

	<p><PluginCountRemovedChart dataPoints={countDataPoints} client:only="svelte" /></p>

	<p>This shows what percentage of plugins, sorted by their release month, have been removed from the community plugin list.</p>

	<p><PluginRemovedByReleaseChart dataPoints={retiredByMonthDataPoints} client:only="svelte" /></p>

